(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:Times New Roman, serif;&amp;#34; %)The failure of environmental justice movements to solve is due to a misplaced focus on liberal politics – electing President Obama has only put a Black face on the White Supremacism of Nuclear Power Policymaking

(% style=&amp;#34;margin-bottom: 0in&amp;#34; %)
