(% style=&amp;#34;margin-bottom: 0in&amp;#34; %)
(% style=&amp;#34;font-family:Times New Roman, serif;&amp;#34; %)The problem is structural, as Black suffering has created the condition of possibility for an advancement of consumption with no paradigm to evaluate it all. There is only one possibility: black trash.

